<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.2">
<l>ariviravu mukiṟkaṇattā lakilpukaiyāl varaiyōṭum</l>
<l>terivariya maṇimāṭat tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>variyaravi ṉaṇaittuyiṉṟu maḻaimatatta ciṟutaṟukaṇ</l>
<l>kariveruva maruppocittāṟ kiḻantēṉeṉ kaṉavaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my thick bangles to the one who, having slept on a striped serpent bed,</l>
<l>Broke the tusk of an elephant with small, tight eyes [and] rain[-like] musth</l>
<l rend="indent">so it was frightened,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram with jeweled mansions where,</l>
<l>Due to smoke from aquila wood and to masses of brown-mottled clouds,</l>
<l rend="indent">discerning them from mountains is difficult.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
